i use Event Notify with Annotation in dubbo2.7.7 version, still can't work


```
    @Reference(interfaceClass = HelloService.class, 
            methods = {
                    @Method(
                            name = "sayHello",
                            oninvoke = "notify.oninvoke",
                            onreturn = "notify.onreturn",
                            onthrow = "notify.onthrow")
            }
    )
    private HelloService helloService;
```

@zyf6303 @Lontten 
https://github.com/liunancun/demo.git
我这个demo里面只是用简单的dubbo依赖，没有用nacos等其他组件

2.7.9 应该修复了该问题，我看到2.7.8的ConfigCenterBasedMetadataReportFactory在2.7.9中没了，
ConfigCenterBasedMetadataReportFactory#resolveURLParameters

    private URL resolveURLParameters(URL url) {
        URL resolvedURL = url.removeParameters(EXPORT_KEY, REFER_KEY);
        if (PATH.equals(getKeyType())) { // Only handles for "PATH" type
            if (isBlank(resolvedURL.getParameter(CONFIG_ROOT_PATH_PARAM_NAME))) {
                resolvedURL = resolvedURL.addParameter(CONFIG_ROOT_PATH_PARAM_NAME, SLASH);
            }
        }
        return resolvedURL;
    }

默认值SLASH应该导致了该问题，在未来的2.7.9中应该没这个问题了

